title: Fort Myers' Gear, Charlotte's Dillon win District 3A-11 cross country titles
text:
Fort Myers' Gear, Charlotte's Dillon win District 3A-11 cross country titles 
Published By: News-press.com - Today 
Fort Myers junior Krissy Gear won her second straight District 3A-11 cross country championship on Friday at Veterans Park in Lehigh
